column2: SELECT    s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.class, s.zWarning, s.snMedian, el.ra1, el.dec1, e.bpt, e.Flux_Hb_#,e.Flux_OIII_#, e.Flux_Ha_#, e.Flux_NII_# into mydb. MyTable_# from mydb.radec2 as el CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjEq( el.ra1, el.dec1, #) AS near  JOIN SpecObjAll as s ON near.specObjID=s.specObjID JOIN emissionLinesPort as e ON near.specObjID=e.specObjID WHERE  s.snMedian >= # AND  s.class = &&& AND   s.zWarning=#
